    "description": "<p>Incanters and intoners who have mastered the art of the warsong, letting them infuse powerful spirits of song upon themselves and their allies.</p>",
    "attacks": "<p><strong>Inflict Violence: Thundering Lute.</strong> Attack all enemies in an area (blast 4) with Faith, all allies in the blast may <strong>fly 2.</strong></p><p><strong>Gambits</strong> [[/r d12]]</p><p><strong>1-3:</strong> Rush &gt; Inflict Violence &gt; <strong>Sing Louder [1]:</strong> Increase the Aura by 1 until the start of the Singer's next riff. Doesn't stack.</p><p><strong>4-6:</strong> Rush &gt; <strong>Dirge [2]:</strong> All allies in the battlefield gain <strong>+1</strong> to Posture and Resilience until the end of the Singer's next riff.</p><p><strong>7-9:</strong> Rush &gt; <strong>Rouse [2]:</strong> All allies in the battlefield gain <strong>+1</strong> to Bravery and Faith until the end of the Singer's next riff.</p><p><strong>10-12: Encore [3]:</strong> After the Singer's Riff, choose another ally, even if they've already riffed. They may riff immediately after the Singer, and gain +1 to their attacks.</p>",
